  "original_title": "\u0db1\u0dd0\u0dad\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dd4\u0db1 \u0db4\u0ddc\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dba\u0dd2 \u0db6\u0dd4\u0daf\u0dd4 \u0db4\u0dd2\u0dc5\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dd4\u0dba\u0dd2 \u0db8\u0dcf \u0d9c\u0dcf\u0dc0: \u0daf\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0db6\u0dba\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "I have lost bark and a Buddha statue: I am afraid to give",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "President's Secretary Mr. Saman Ekanayake has handed over further investigation to the Secret Police regarding a phone call received by the Presidential Secretariat about a Buddha statue and a stock of books stolen from the residence of President Ranil Wickramasinghe.",
        "A call to the public telephone number of the President's office said that the Buddha statue and books were stolen on the day the President's house was set on fire and that they need to be returned.",
        "The person who made the phone call to the President's office said that keeping the stolen Buddha statue and books with them is a matter of fear and should be returned to the owner.",
        "The caller said that the Buddha statue and books are safe.",
        "He has said that he wants to call the President's Secretary and the official who took the call from the President's Office has handed over the message to the President's Secretary and handed over further investigations to the Secret Police."
      ],
